1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 1=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=You Must Be
the Grand Princess's Toy Boy=

4
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:50,380
(Wuyue tribe · Spring, Year 6 of Yuanqi)

5
00:00:53,790 --> 00:00:56,350
Zhaoli, we've shared a bed.

6
00:00:56,350 --> 00:00:57,920
What should you call me then?

7
00:00:58,030 --> 00:00:59,590
Honey.

8
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:04,150
(I'm about to see his face.)

9
00:01:04,150 --> 00:01:05,790
(Don't wake up.)

10
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:12,150
(In the dream,
I seem to like him very much.)

11
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:14,020
(Wu Zhaoli, a healer)
(I called him honey.)

12
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,480
(I've had this dream so many times.)

13
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,070
(Yet his face is always hidden.)

14
00:01:17,350 --> 00:01:18,640
(Who is he, really?)

15
00:01:22,060 --> 00:01:22,900
If I could obtain

16
00:01:22,910 --> 00:01:24,790
the Fengwu Bracelet
that reveals the past,

17
00:01:25,070 --> 00:01:27,120
I could learn who he is.

18
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,120
Wu Zhaoli.

19
00:01:28,250 --> 00:01:29,950
The Grand Princess has sent
for medicine.

20
00:01:29,950 --> 00:01:30,790
I'm coming.

21
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,000
Dry this separately.

22
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:37,940
Alright.

23
00:01:37,950 --> 00:01:38,790
Mind the heat.

24
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,310
- Relax.
- This looks about right.

25
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,320
Alright.

26
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,710
What are you waiting for?

27
00:01:47,430 --> 00:01:49,540
Milord, this is the medicine
for the Grand Princess.

28
00:01:49,590 --> 00:01:50,480
Please take a look.

29
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,870
I have prepared all of it.

30
00:01:58,710 --> 00:01:59,750
This was secretly crafted

31
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:02,280
at the Grand Princess's request.

32
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:04,500
(Li Hucong, attendant
of the Grand Princess)

33
00:02:05,710 --> 00:02:07,120
As per our agreement,

34
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,630
when may I borrow

35
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:10,360
the Fengwu Bracelet for a while?

36
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,040
The Grand Princess has said it.

37
00:02:12,150 --> 00:02:13,800
You may borrow the Bracelet.

38
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,310
But you must fetch it yourself.

39
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,800
What are you doing?

40
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:22,550
- Let go!
- What are you doing?

41
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:24,190
That's not what you said before.

42
00:02:24,190 --> 00:02:25,030
Let go of Zhaoli!

43
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,493
Grandmother! Grandmother!

44
00:02:26,504 --> 00:02:28,510
(Zhaoli's grandmother)
Zhaoli! What are you doing?

45
00:02:28,510 --> 00:02:29,830
- Don't move!
- Don't hurt her!

46
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:30,650
I'll go with you.

47
00:02:30,650 --> 00:02:31,900
- Zhaoli!
- I'll go with you.

48
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:33,120
- Zhaoli!
- Grandmother!

49
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,440
- What's going on?
- Grandmother!

50
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:35,440
Where are you taking her?

51
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,830
Did Zhaoli anger the Grand Princess?

52
00:02:36,830 --> 00:02:37,830
- Zhaoli!
- Grandmother!

53
00:02:37,860 --> 00:02:39,800
Grandmother, I'm fine.
Don't worry about me.

54
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,470
- Zhaoli!
- I'll be back soon.

55
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:42,310
Release her!

56
00:02:42,310 --> 00:02:44,150
- Grandmother, I'll be back soon.
- Zhaoli!

57
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,520
You...

58
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:49,800
Let me go!

59
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,840
Why have you brought me here?

60
00:02:58,190 --> 00:02:59,460
The Princess has given the order.

61
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,910
The Bracelet is a rare treasure.

62
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:03,630
If you wish to borrow it,

63
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:06,360
it depends on whether you can consummate
the union tonight.

64
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,870
Consummate the union?

65
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,870
The Grand Princess

66
00:03:10,980 --> 00:03:12,420
is forcing someone into consummation?

67
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,710
How utterly absurd.

68
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:17,710
Let go!

69
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:18,920
Let go of me!

70
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:28,840
You have only four hours.

71
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,680
Don't go!

72
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,470
Could it be that the Grand Princess

73
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,030
is unable to bear children

74
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,400
and wants me to consummate
with her toy boy?

75
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:04,360
Absolutely not!

76
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,900
He's clearly
under the influence of a drug.

77
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,800
I must get out.

78
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:14,750
Open the door!

79
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:16,560
Help!

80
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,480
Let me out of here!

81
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,680
Open the door.

82
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:22,590
So noisy.

83
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,190
Milord, please spare my life.

84
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,360
I've been poisoned.

85
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,190
Please, don't hurt me.

86
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,680
Once I get out of here,

87
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,950
I'll surely repay your kindness.

88
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,870
Did Ye Li send you?

89
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,630
You're the one from my dreams?

90
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:47,680
I'm not.

91
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,680
Is it you?

92
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:56,190
Let me take a look at you.

93
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,360
If you dare defy the order,

94
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,530
don't blame the Grand Princess
for flaying you alive.

95
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:10,140
(Everlasting Joy)

96
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:14,030
Your Highness.

97
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:16,100
Each time the Frostbite Curse flares up,

98
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:17,850
the ruler would rather endure the pain

99
00:05:17,850 --> 00:05:19,680
than touch the women you sent in.

100
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,170
This time, I fear it will be the same.

101
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:24,170
This time, it's different.

102
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:25,560
(Ye Li, Grand Princess)

103
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,040
That healer has a rare constitution.

104
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,630
With the love potion,

105
00:05:28,630 --> 00:05:30,920
she can surely ease his Frostbite Curse.

106
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,430
Watch closely.

107
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,750
You are not him.

108
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,040
Not him.

109
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,430
Let go of me.

110
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,120
You shameless rogue!

111
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,750
If you don't wish to suffer,

112
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:54,430
then stay still.

113
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:56,190
What are you trying to do?

114
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,320
Helping you finish your task.

115
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:09,860
(Everlasting Joy)

116
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:15,680
You... you bit me!

117
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,160
You can detoxify the love poison?

118
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,120
How did you manage that?

119
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,040
Put away your curiosity.

120
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,800
Leave at once.

121
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:56,240
I'm not one to owe favors to anyone.

122
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,630
Since you saved my life,

123
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,430
I'll return the favor.

124
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,390
Then we'll be even.

125
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,080
What is this?

126
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:08,920
A feign-death pill.

127
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,830
My secret prescription.

128
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:13,390
Judging by your looks,

129
00:07:13,390 --> 00:07:15,750
you must be
the Grand Princess's toy boy.

130
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,760
Her toy boy?

131
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,950
Rather than stay under her twisted hand,

132
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,070
enduring torment,

133
00:07:21,510 --> 00:07:25,000
why not live freely on your own?

134
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,140
Once you leave the Palace,

135
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,750
find an honest way to make a living.

136
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:34,600
Guards, come!

137
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:36,070
The toy boy is dead!

138
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:37,920
Take me to the Grand Princess at once!

139
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:54,480
Greetings, Your Highness.

140
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,360
As you ordered,

141
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,800
I had the consummation with that man.

142
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:02,040
Please honor your promise

143
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,510
by lending the Bracelet

144
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:05,160
to me.

145
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:07,750
I let you consummate with him

146
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,680
to ease his suffering.

147
00:08:09,870 --> 00:08:11,120
But you ended up

148
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,000
making him faint.

149
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:14,030
Guards!

150
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,920
Take her life in punishment.

151
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,160
Wait! Wait!

152
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,560
Your Highness,

153
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,070
you're clearly the ones at fault.

154
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:27,040
I did exactly as you asked.

155
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,870
Why am I the one to be executed?

156
00:08:29,070 --> 00:08:29,920
Besides,

157
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,160
as the Grand Princess,

158
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,030
how could you...

159
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:37,660
(Ying Du, ruler of Puluo State)

160
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,360
(Why the sudden whip marks?)

161
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:51,960
(Why is my power)

162
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,510
(unable to heal even a wound?)

163
00:09:08,030 --> 00:09:09,840
(She shares a spiritual link with me.)

164
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:16,120
(So foolish)

165
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,320
(to have someone pull your hair.)

166
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:25,030
How could you

167
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:27,080
lash me just like this?

168
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:31,200
Your status doesn't give you
the right to trample lives!

169
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,600
Sharp-tongued.

170
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,550
Since you are of no use,

171
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,960
you may go to hell.

172
00:09:43,740 --> 00:09:48,390
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

173
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:55,190
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

174
00:09:56,650 --> 00:09:59,930
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

175
00:09:59,930 --> 00:10:02,830
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

176
00:10:03,350 --> 00:10:08,640
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

177
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:12,340
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

178
00:10:12,690 --> 00:10:15,040
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

179
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:19,080
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

180
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:21,460
♪And that is enough♪

181
00:10:21,460 --> 00:10:25,250
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

182
00:10:25,460 --> 00:10:28,220
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

183
00:10:28,590 --> 00:10:34,340
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

184
